注意:
  1. commit 信息需要指定为当前版本号
  2. 修改版本号
    "./src/ver/CMakeLists.txt" => set(VERSION "1.x")
  3. .github/workflows/build.yaml
    3.1. 添加程序运行缺少的依赖库
    - name: Compiling
      shell: bash
      run: |
        cd build && ninja aseprite
        curl -s -L https://github.com/charlesbases/aseprite/releases/download/v1.3.7/libcrypto-1_1-x64.dll --output bin/libcrypto-1_1-x64.dll
    3.2. 添加 step 导出编译文件
    - uses: actions/upload-artifact@v3
      with:
        name: aseprite
        path: D:/a/aseprite/aseprite/build/bin


